---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import LegalPage from '../../components/LegalPage.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { t } from '../../i18n/index';

const lang = 'en';
const i = t(lang);
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Translay" description="Translay Privacy Policy" lang={lang}>
  <Navbar lang={lang} nav={i.nav} />
  <LegalPage title="Privacy Policy" lastUpdated="Last updated: February 2026">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>Translay ("we", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use the Translay application.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect and How We Use It</h2>
    <p>We collect and use only what is necessary to provide the app:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>On-device only:</strong> Screenshots and images are processed locally by OCR. They are never uploaded.</li>
      <li><strong>Translation:</strong> Only the OCR-extracted text (no images) is sent to the translation service to provide translations.</li>
      <li><strong>AI follow-up feature:</strong> Only when you use this feature, we send the data described below to DeepSeek (our AI service provider), after you have given permission.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage count:</strong> A usage counter is synced via iCloud to manage free-tier limits. We do not collect personally identifiable information.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party AI Service — What We Send and Who Receives It</h2>
    <p>When you use the <strong>AI follow-up</strong> feature, the app may send the following to <strong>DeepSeek</strong> (our third-party AI service provider):</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>What data:</strong> The text of your follow-up question and the translation context (e.g. source and translated text) needed to answer it. No images or screenshots are sent.</li>
      <li><strong>Who receives it:</strong> DeepSeek. You will see this name in the app when you enable the feature and before any data is sent.</li>
      <li><strong>When we send it:</strong> Only after you have been clearly informed and have given your permission. The app will not send data to the AI service without your consent.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not store your AI conversations. Transmissions to DeepSeek use encrypted channels (HTTPS/TLS). Our agreement with DeepSeek requires that they protect your data with the same or equal level of protection and do not use it for training their models on your content.</p>

    <h2>Information Collection and Use (Detail)</h2>
    <h3>Local Processing</h3>
    <p>Translay's OCR (Optical Character Recognition) runs entirely on your device. Your screenshots and images are never uploaded to any server.</p>

    <h3>Translation Service</h3>
    <p>To provide translations, we send OCR-recognized text (text only, no images) through encrypted channels to the translation service (DeepL). This text is not stored or used for other purposes.</p>

    <h3>AI Follow-Up Feature</h3>
    <p>When you use the AI follow-up feature, the app will explain what data is sent and to whom (DeepSeek), and will ask for your permission before sending any data. Only after you consent will translation-related text be sent through encrypted channels to DeepSeek. We do not store your conversations.</p>

    <h3>Usage Data</h3>
    <p>We only sync your usage counter via iCloud to manage free quotas. We do not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>All network transmissions use HTTPS/TLS encryption. We do not maintain a user database or store any translation content or personal information.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Translay uses the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>DeepL</strong> — Translation service. Only OCR text is sent; not stored for other purposes.</li>
      <li><strong>DeepSeek</strong> — AI follow-up feature only, when you have given permission. We require that they provide the same or equal protection for your data and do not use it to train models.</li>
      <li><strong>Apple iCloud</strong> — Usage count synchronization.</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — API proxy and security.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Translay is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updated policies will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: <a href="mailto:bob.wang@imyway.cn" class="text-blue-primary hover:underline">bob.wang@imyway.cn</a></p>
  </LegalPage>
  <Footer lang={lang} footer={i.footer} />
</BaseLayout>
